<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="features-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why this app exists</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Your music taste deserves to be seen. Quietly, automatically, without lifting a finger.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon spotify">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.4 0 0 5.4 0 12s5.4 12 12 12 12-5.4 12-12S18.66 0 12 0zm5.521 17.34c-.24.359-.66.48-1.021.24-2.82-1.74-6.36-2.101-10.561-1.141-.418.122-.779-.179-.899-.539-.12-.421.18-.78.54-.9 4.56-1.021 8.52-.6 11.64 1.32.42.18.479.659.301 1.02zm1.44-3.3c-.301.42-.841.6-1.262.3-3.239-1.98-8.159-2.58-11.939-1.38-.479.12-1.02-.12-1.14-.6-.12-.48.12-1.021.6-1.141C9.6 9.9 15 10.561 18.72 12.84c.361.181.54.78.241 1.2zm.12-3.36C15.24 8.4 8.82 8.16 5.16 9.301c-.6.179-1.2-.181-1.38-.721-.18-.601.18-1.2.72-1.381 4.26-1.26 11.28-1.02 15.721 1.621.539.3.719 1.02.419 1.56-.299.421-1.02.599-1.559.3z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Spotify aware</h3>
        <p>Polls the Spotify API for your currently playing track. No browser extensions, no hacks. Just your real playback state.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon teams">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm4.95 15.95c-.367.367-.85.55-1.45.55s-1.083-.183-1.45-.55c-.367-.367-.55-.85-.55-1.45s.183-1.083.55-1.45c.367-.367.85-.55 1.45-.55s1.083.183 1.45.55c.367.367.55.85.55 1.45s-.183 1.083-.55 1.45zm-7.9 0c-.367.367-.85.55-1.45.55s-1.083-.183-1.45-.55C5.783 15.583 5.6 15.1 5.6 14.5s.183-1.083.55-1.45c.367-.367.85-.55 1.45-.55s1.083.183 1.45.55c.367.367.55.85.55 1.45s-.183 1.083-.55 1.45zM17.5 8.5c0 .833-.292 1.542-.875 2.125-.583.583-1.292.875-2.125.875s-1.542-.292-2.125-.875C11.792 10.042 11.5 9.333 11.5 8.5s.292-1.542.875-2.125C12.958 5.792 13.667 5.5 14.5 5.5s1.542.292 2.125.875C17.208 6.958 17.5 7.667 17.5 8.5z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Teams integrated</h3>
        <p>Sets your Microsoft Teams status message via Microsoft Graph. Uses delegated permissions&mdash;no admin consent needed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon auto">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Set it and forget it</h3>
        <p>Once connected, it runs in your system tray. New track? Status updates. Playback stopped? Status clears. Zero interaction needed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon format">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Custom status format</h3>
        <p>Use <code>{'{artist}'}</code> and <code>{'{title}'}</code> placeholders to craft your perfect status message. Add emojis, text, whatever you like.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon private">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Your data stays yours</h3>
        <p>Runs entirely on your machine. Credentials stored locally, never shared. No analytics, no telemetry, no cloud middleman.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon oss">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Open source</h3>
        <p>MIT licensed. Built with .NET 10 and Avalonia UI. PRs welcome. The code is on <a href="https://github.com/craigvincent/spotify_nowplaying" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

